description:
Expand your track list with the Party Classics Vol. 1 Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Diana Ross "Upside Down"
• Madness "Our House"
• UB40 "(I Can't Help) Falling In Love With You"
• The Cranberries "Zombie"
• Queen "Crazy Little Thing Called Love"
name: Let's Sing - Party Classics Vol. 1 Song Pack
